snippet.title: Mount Your Friends 3D Customization and Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist and Follow Mount Your Friends 3D on Steam! Releases Feb 23rd!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/441010/Mount_Your_Friends_3D_A_Hard_Man_is_Good_to_Climb/

Mount Your Friends 3D is coming and it’s time to start styling. Become a master of mounting in Mount Your Friends 3D: A Hard Man is Good to Climb. Express your fashionable side with a variety of skins and trails for your team. Change your face or use your webcam to snap a selfie for perfect, pristine self-representation in the competitive world of mounting. Character customization has never been so easy!

Music
"The Descent"
Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
